  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "\n<p><b>Type:</b> Ninjutsu </p>\n<p><b>Rank:</b> 5 (Spell Level 3)</p>\n<p><b>Chakra Cost:</b> 2</p>\n\n<p><b>Learn DC:</b> 18 | <b>Successes:</b> 3</p>\n<p><b>Perform:</b> 6 | <b>Perform DC:</b> 18</p>\n\n<p><b>Components:</b> C, E, M</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p>You fire a web of sticky spider silk to hinder or capture a foe. If a Small or smaller creature is hit by 1 or 2 webs, it becomes @Condition[entangled]{entangled} or immobilized, respectively. For Medium creatures, the same is true if hit by 2 or 4 webs. For Large, the numbers are 4 and 8. The entanglement lasts 2d4+1 rounds, and two consecutive Strength or Escape Artist checks (DC 15) can be made to break free. The immobilization lasts for 2d6 rounds, and three consecutive Strength or Escape Artist checks (DC 18) can be made to break free.</p>\n\n<hr><p><b>Empower:</b> Spend 2 Chakra to fire an additional web, up to 1 per 3 levels. Each web can target the same or a different creature.</p>\n\n",
      "summary": "",
      "instructions": ""
    },
